name: Deer Seized by US Government
description: Baby was wrongfully seized by the Pennsylvania Gaming Commission from his family. Help spread awareness. Community Driven Initiative to save the life of Baby the Deer which was wrongfully taken from it's home in Pittsburgh. Tammy said on her post "So I needed him in so many different ways, just as he needed me. So to the ones who said why didn't I stop them or I do more. I did what I could, it killed me that I couldn't do more for my loving deer."
